Our work is also
expensive and many of you

00:04:44.690 --> 00:04:48.530
here today number among
our supporters, for which I

00:04:48.530 --> 00:04:50.570
want to applaud you.

00:04:50.570 --> 00:04:51.257
Thank you.

00:04:51.257 --> 00:04:52.171
[APPLAUSE]

